Input:
```json
{
  "message": "Hello, I am John Doe, the CEO of XYZ Corp. You can reach me at john.doe@xyzcorp.com for any further queries."
}
```

Output:
```json
{
  "contacts": [
    {
      "name": "John Doe",
      "email": "john.doe@xyzcorp.com",
      "role": "CEO of XYZ Corp"
    }
  ]
}
```

